xdg-desktop-portal-lxqt-1.3.0 / 2025-11-05
==========================================
 * Use native systemd service.
 * Fixed building with Qt 6.10.

xdg-desktop-portal-lxqt-1.2.0 / 2025-04-17
==========================================
 * Don't fork a child process in the portal's service.

xdg-desktop-portal-lxqt-1.1.0 / 2024-11-05
==========================================
 * Added the conf file `lxqt-portals.conf`.

xdg-desktop-portal-lxqt-1.0.2 / 2024-05-04
==========================================
 * Fixed the initial path (the credit goes to the KDE team for their solution in `xdg-desktop-portal-kde`).

xdg-desktop-portal-lxqt-1.0.1 / 2024-04-18
==========================================
 * Removed the redundant `qt5x11extra` dependency.

xdg-desktop-portal-lxqt-1.0.0 / 2024-04-17
==========================================
 * Support `current_folder` when opening files.
 * Transfer ownership of options widget.
 * Convert mimetype filters to name filters.
 * Ported to Qt6.

xdg-desktop-portal-lxqt-0.5.0 / 2023-11-05
==========================================
 * Made it depending on libfm-qt-1.4.0 and bumped the version.

xdg-desktop-portal-lxqt-0.4.0 / 2023-04-15
==========================================
 * Bumped the version

xdg-desktop-portal-lxqt-0.3.0 / 2022-11-05
==========================================
 * Updated and improved `README.md`.

xdg-desktop-portal-lxqt-0.2.0 / 2022-04-15
==========================================
 * Use Fm:FileDialogHelper (apps using `xdg-portal` will behave like the native Qt apps under LXQt).

xdg-desktop-portal-lxqt-0.1.0 / 2022-02-03
==========================================
 * Initial release.
